data.description: This beautiful two-story home will win your heart. There is more than 2,200 square feet of living area in this four-bedroom, two-bathroom house, including a finished basement with central air and heat. A spacious master suite with tray ceilings and built-ins is part of the split floor layout. Located in the center of Little Rock. The roof was replaced in 2019, the HVAC system was replaced in 2022, and the new flooring 2023. Only the buyer who acts NOW will be able to purchase this property. Great investment property! Don't Miss Out on This Opportunity!  Property Sold As Is.
